timelineItems.text: 27’ - Maund booked for mistimed tackle on Chavez … #RSL up 1-0 at #ATL

timelineItems.name: ATLSilverbacks
timelineItems.text: 30' - Another close chance for the Silverbacks, as Sandoval heads just wide. 0-1 #ATLvsRSL #USOC2014 #NASLTheCup

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: 40’ - PHENOMENAL from the #watergato … #RSL 1 : 1 at ATL

timelineItems.name: ATLSilverbacks
timelineItems.text: Shoutout to the @AtlantaUltras, @TerminusLegion, and Westside 109 for being loud and bringing big numbers tonight! #ATLvsRSL #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: 44’ - Gavin booked for takedown of Mulholland … #RSL 1 : 1 at ATL

timelineItems.comment: First Half ends, Atlanta Silverbacks 1, Real Salt Lake 1.

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: #ATLvRSL HALFTIME. A miscommunication in the back field leads to a Robbie Findley goal for #RSL.… http://t.co/zYn3sLBkm1

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: HT: #RSL 1 : 1 at ATL in @usopencup play … tune into @espn700 for interview with GM Garth Lagerwey

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: 2nd half #USOC2014 about to kick, no changes to #RSL XI … 1-1 at ATL

timelineItems.comment: Second Half begins Atlanta Silverbacks 1, Real Salt Lake 1.

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: 55’ - Burgos booked after cleaning out Stertzer … #RSL 1 : 1 at ATL

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: 60’ - ATTINELLA with back-to-back set-piece saves … 1-1 #RSL at ATL

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: 63’ - Plata / Velasquez in for #RSL, Gil & Sandoval out … 1-1 at ATL #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: 65’ - Salcedo booked for taking down Cruz on breakaway … #RSL 1-1 at ATL #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: 73’ - STERTZER clears header off line to preserve 1-1 score … #RSL at ATL #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: ATLSilverbacks
timelineItems.text: 73' - CLEARED OFF THE LINE! Harlley puts a header on frame and #RSL's Stertzer clears it off the goal line to safety. #ATLvsRSL #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: 77’ - Garcia in for Stertzer, #RSL 1-1 at ATL #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: 80’ - ATTINELLA stones Sandoval breakaway #RSL 1-1 at ATL #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: ATLSilverbacks
timelineItems.text: 8' - Findley with a nice half-volley that hits the side netting. Not far off from the former US international. 0-0 #ATLvsRSL #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: ATLSilverbacks
timelineItems.text: 84' - Harlley earns a corner kick for the Silverbacks. Cruz will take it, but he's in no rush to get over there. 1-1 #ATLvsRSL #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: 83’ - Chances from Mulholland and Garcia go wanting, no equalizer here … #RSL 1-1 at ATL #USOC2014

timelineItems.name: ATLSilverbacks
timelineItems.text: Player intros underway in Atlanta. #ATLvsRSL #USOC2014 #NASLTheCup

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: 10’ - FINDLEY GOAL #RSL!!!

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: FT: #RSL 1 : 2 at ATL … 10’ lead on Findley goal dissolves on road in #USOC2014

timelineItems.comment: Second Half ends, Atlanta Silverbacks 2, Real Salt Lake 1.

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: FINAL A late #ATL goal eliminates #RSL from this year's US Open Cup. http://t.co/FyBc6dX8jf
